Developer Notes
---------------

See README-HACKING in this directory.

What's different from SoZ 2.3.x?
--------------------------------

This section enumerates the notable differences from SoZ 2.3.x.

- Written in Java

- Lucene server is not a separate process.

  Since the implementation language is Java there is no need
  to run the Lucene server in a separate process.
